  <div style="margin-top: 40px;">
    <h3>English Introduction</h3>
    <p>
      Quanzhou Hengyuande Paper Products Co., Ltd. is a professional manufacturer
      specializing in the production and processing of household paper products.
      For over ten years, we have adhered to quality as our core value and environmental
      protection as our guiding principle, providing safe, soft, and reliable paper products
      to customers worldwide.<br><br>
      With advanced production equipment, a strict quality control system, and an experienced
      technical team, we continuously enhance our product performance and service standards,
      earning long-term trust from our partners.<br><br>
      Hengyuande remains committed to sustainability by optimizing production processes
      to minimize environmental impact. We believe that consistent quality and sincere service
      are the keys to long-term success.
    </p>
